&lt;h4>NumPy 스타일&lt;span class="hx-absolute -hx-mt-20" id="numpy-스타일">&lt;/span>
&lt;a href="#numpy-%ec%8a%a4%ed%83%80%ec%9d%bc" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section">&lt;/a>&lt;/h4>&lt;p>특징:&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>과학 계산 커뮤니티에서 널리 사용됩니다.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>매개변수와 반환값을 명확하게 구조화합니다.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>수학적 표현이나 복잡한 매개변수를 설명하기에 적합합니다.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Google 스타일보다 더 형식적인 구조를 가집니다.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>예시:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="hextra-code-block hx-relative hx-mt-6 first:hx-mt-0 hx-group/code">
&lt;div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="k">def&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nf">numpy_style&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">param1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nb">str&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">param2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nb">int&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">-&amp;gt;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nb">dict&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;
